2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The use of model checking procedures and the extension of fluid approaches to more sophisticated interrogations of models suggest the involvement of AI techniques.
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the analysis of a system (Markov population model) and its behaviour, which falls under the scope of systems and control.
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper may involve the use of algorithms for efficient checking of properties, which falls under the scope of data structures and algorithms.
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The use of fluid approaches and model checking procedures may involve the use of machine learning techniques for analysis and prediction.
